## Section 3: Constraints
1. Must use TypeScript
2. Node.js 18+ required
3. Performance: < 100ms startup time

Special characters: "quotes", 'apostrophes', \`backticks\`, \\backslashes\\`;

            await manager.updatePhase(
                conversation.id,
                "plan",
